race.description: Ladbrokes Mates Mode Pots 5Th Grade H
race.comment: TOUGH ENOUGH (5) stalked the lead and fought on well to finish 2.25 lengths away in second (30.86) at Q Parklands in a Grade 5 over 520m. Can find winning form. BAD BOY ELVIS (1) is looking to continue his winning ways off a sharp 16.65 success in a Grade 5 at this track. Should be in this for a long way. NOAKI UNO (6) winner two starts back at this track over 300m in 16.46. Last start finished out of the placings when 4th over 300m at this track in Grade 5. Had won two on end prior to the latest effort. Can atone. Something for the Multiples: BIG OPERATOR (7)
